# Layout width

| Mode (chat) | Class | Width | Use for |
|-------------|-------|-------|---------|
| **bleed** | `layout--bleed` | `100vw` (browser edges) | Hero images, theme headlines only |
| **full-width** | `layout--full` | 100% of centered shell (max 1920px) | Banners inside shell |
| **wide** | default / `layout--wide` | centered shell, max 1920px | Page column |
| **narrow** | `layout--narrow` | `min(1400px, 72.9% of shell)` centered | Media stacks, text blocks |

- `body` uses `width: min(100%, 1920px)` + `margin-inline: auto` — equal gutters on ultrawide (`html` background shows both sides).
- **Do not** put `layout--bleed` on whole sections with mixed content — only headlines/heroes. Section bg uses `::before` at `100vw` where needed.
